messages.message: Hey Team :wave::slightly_smiling_face: I remember that we've discussed about having engineering office hours each week to give all of us the chance to ask questions and learn from each other. Many times I stumble upon something that would much better fit into a 5min discussion than a lengthy Slack post. Is it still planned to introduce Eng. Office Hours in the near feature?
hey kevin! let me think about this for the org and get back to you!
